description:
This is a 59 minute workout called '60 MIN ENDURANCE CHALLENGE | Treadmill Follow Along!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.

Original workout description: This one is TOUGH! We are going to hit it hard and stick through it for 1 full hour! An Endurance Challenge!!

1 hour of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!
